# Release pipeline edits

Read `engineering-devops-automator` skill before changing these files.

## Checklist

1. If `Dockerfile` copies `package-lock.json` for `npm ci`, confirm `.dockerignore` does **not** exclude it
2. `release.yml` SBOM step uses stdout redirect: `npm sbom ... > sbom.cdx.json`
3. Run `docker build -f packaging/docker/Dockerfile .` before any release tag
4. Run `review-bugbot` on the diff

See [docs/agent-workflow.md](../agent-workflow.md).
